attributes.description:
This histogram shows the distribution of students based on their Math scores by grouping them into score ranges (0–10, 10–20, …, 90–100).
It helps identify how many students fall into each score range and highlights overall performance trends in Mathematics.

attributes.description: This dashboard analyzes students' academic performance based on gender, subject scores, and background factors such as parental education and test preparation. It helps identify trends and patterns to support educational insights and decision making.
